Loss of Y chromosome: An emerging next-generation biomarker for disease 
prediction and early detection?

Guo X(1), Li J(2), Xue J(3), Fenech M(4), Wang X(5).

Author information:
(1)School of Life Sciences, Yunnan Normal University, Kunming, Yunnan, 650500, 
China; Yunnan Environmental Mutagen Society, Kunming, Yunnan, 650500, China. 
