Lifetime risk of cardiovascular disease and life expectancy with and without 
cardiovascular disease according to changes in metabolic syndrome status.

Li D(1), Wang L(1), Zhou Z(1), Song L(1), Chen S(2), Yang Y(1), Hu Y(3), Wang 
Y(1), Wu S(4), Tian Y(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Maternal and Child Health, School of Public Health, Tongji 
Medical College, Huazhong University of Science and Technology, No.13 Hangkong 
Road, Wuhan, 430030, China; Ministry of Education Key Laboratory of Environment 
and Health, And State Key Laboratory of Environmental Health (Incubating), 
